Wage theft and life expectancy inequities in the United States: A simulation 
study.

Eisenberg-Guyot J(1), Keyes KM(2), Prins SJ(3), McKetta S(2), Mooney SJ(4), 
Bates LM(2), Wall MM(5), Platt JM(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Epidemiology, Mailman School of Public Health, Columbia 
University, NY, USA. Electronic address: je2433@cumc.columbia.edu.
(2)Department of Epidemiology, Mailman School of Public Health, Columbia 
